#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains settings which control the appearance of &dolphin; on "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"Kelompok ini berisi pengaturan yang mengendalikan penampilan &dolphin; saat "
"pemulaian."

#. Tag: screeninfo
